---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="ZENYARE by QINGDAO ZHENGYA RUBBER INDUSTRIAL CO., LTD - Motorcycle Tires & Inner Tubes"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>About ZENYARE</h1>
    <p>
      ZENYARE is a professional manufacturer of motorcycle tires and motorcycle inner tubes,
      operated by <strong>QINGDAO ZHENGYA RUBBER INDUSTRIAL CO., LTD</strong>.
      This website (Tire of Moto) shares practical knowledge about tire sizing, tube valves,
      fitment tips, and sourcing guidance for distributors and motorcycle users.
    </p>
  </section>

  <hr />

  <section class="grid">
    <div class="card" style="grid-column: span 12">
      <h2 style="margin:0 0 8px">Company Profile</h2>
      <p style="margin:0;color:var(--muted)">
        QINGDAO ZHENGYA RUBBER INDUSTRIAL CO., LTD focuses on stable quality, consistent production,
        and long-term cooperation. Our products are developed for daily commuting, commercial use,
        and varied road conditions across different markets.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="grid-column: span 6">
      <h2 style="margin:0 0 8px">Main Products</h2>
      <ul style="margin:0;padding-left:18px">
        <li>Motorcycle Tires (TT / TL)</li>
        <li>Motorcycle Inner Tubes (Butyl / Natural rubber options)</li>
        <li>Common valve types: TR4 / TR13 / AV</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="grid-column: span 6">
      <h2 style="margin:0 0 8px">What We Share Here</h2>
      <ul style="margin:0;padding-left:18px">
        <li>Tire size explanation (metric & inch sizes)</li>
        <li>Tube selection checklist (size / valve / angle)</li>
        <li>Installation & maintenance tips</li>
        <li>Buying and sourcing guidance for wholesale customers</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="grid-column: span 12">
      <h2 style="margin:0 0 8px">Quality & Compliance</h2>
      <p style="margin:0;color:var(--muted)">
        Quality management and compliance documentation are handled carefully for export markets.
        The actual certification scope depends on specific tire models and destination requirements.
        If you need compliance support, please contact us with your target market, tire sizes, and patterns.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="grid-column: span 6">
      <h2 style="margin:0 0 8px">Cooperation Focus</h2>
      <p style="margin:0;color:var(--muted)">
        We support distributors, wholesalers, and importers with stable supply, clear specifications,
        and professional communication for long-term business growth.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="grid-column: span 6">
      <h2 style="margin:0 0 8px">Brand Commitment</h2>
      <p style="margin:0;color:var(--muted)">
        ZENYARE is committed to delivering reliable motorcycle tire and tube solutions with
        consistent performance, controlled quality, and responsible service.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr />

  <section class="grid">
    <div class="card" style="grid-column: span 12">
      <h2 style="margin:0 0 8px">Contact</h2>
      <p class="meta" style="margin:0">
        For inquiry, please visit the <a href="/contact">Contact</a> page and send your required sizes,
        quantity, destination port, and target market.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
